name: mikroe.click.buckboost4
short_description: Buck-Boost 4 Click is a compact add-on board that contains a buck-boost DC/DC converter with four integrated MOSFETs. This board features the TPS55289, a buck-boost converter from Texas Instruments. It can deliver on its output voltages from 0.8 up to 22V, from the input voltage in a range of 3 up to 30V. The output voltage can be programmed in 10mV steps.
